{"tid":1155305,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普本周或簽行政命令 封殺華為等中國電訊設備","createTime":"2019-05-15T00:44:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T05:00:15.000Z","uid":3090,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fb56317844cd4213ebbbf48b877b27f2081fb4ae","tid":1155305,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T00:44:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aywy94h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faywy94h.png&h=351823da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n傳特朗普本周可能簽署針對華為的行政命令。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n路透社周二引述三名美國官員報道，總統特朗普可能本周簽署一項針對中國電訊巨企華為的行政命令。<br />\n<br />\n該行政命令將援引《國際緊急經濟權力法》（The International Emergency Economic Powers Act，IEEPA），禁止美國企業使用由威脅美國安全的公司所製造的電訊設備。<br />\n<br />\nIEEPA讓總統有權在「威脅國家的緊急狀況下」管制貿易，指示商務部會同其他部門草擬執行計劃。<br />\n<br />\n美國一直指華為的設備令美國安全面臨風險，命令不會點名國家或公司，但將為美國禁止企業與華為做生意鋪路。<br />\n<br />\n近日中美貿易戰升級，若特朗普本周簽署該項行政命令，時機可謂十分微妙。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士指，該命令已考慮逾一年，並已一再推遲，而且仍有可能再推遲。<br />\n<br />\n路透社"},{"pid":"0fbfbb583fccf17c97e368139bb56a83ac61d81a","tid":1155305,"uid":221819,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T00:50:12.000Z","msg":"有本事就全球禁用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我們吃草也不怕"},{"pid":"a8aeab88ee094d18ab272038ddfd8211ac1fcf93","tid":1155305,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T00:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f831ba7bcb0ee743ea35e3097e7934bf539a5f12","tid":1155305,"uid":65300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:00:35.000Z","msg":"侵侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90735eaf72c777b81a86df2a439361641f2df61e","tid":1155305,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"s